@startuml
!include styling-template.puml

title Basic PlantUML Diagram

actor User

package "GitHub-Inspired Example" {
  component "Frontend" as Frontend
  component "API" as Api
  database "Database" as Db
}

User --> Frontend : opens page
Frontend --> Api : requests data
Api --> Db : reads records
Api --> Frontend : returns response

note right of Api
  Example diagram using
  the shared styling template.
end note

@enduml
